<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l25">Raban hofwart von Kırcheim vnſers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l26"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von vvırcʒburg <expan>hofmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l27"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>hofmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l28"><expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> einr <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> her vor Sacʒ eın pferd 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> der </del> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lorn</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l29">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> einr das <expan>aufgefange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüll <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l30"><expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu was vns deſmals niht wıſſend dauon . ſo waren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l31">auch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> awſʒ dem her dennoch niht <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r1l32"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır ſeıd vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> fleıſſıg darnach fragen laſſen </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_333" id="165v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l1">Vnd ıſt vns ʒu wıſſen <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ etlıch der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein fremd Pferd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l2">haben mıt den <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır dauon reden laſſen / dıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l3">Jn <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> her . ein fremd Pfeͣrd <expan>ʒugeloffe<ex>n</ex></expan> keͣme das <expan>fıenge<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe auf vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l4"><expan>weſte<ex>n</ex></expan> niht wes es <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / vnd <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ ſıe allweg in der meynung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l5"><expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch noch ſeyn . <expan>kom<ex>m</ex></expan> der des das pferd ſey <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l6">von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der des ware <expan>wortʒaıche<ex>n</ex></expan> bring vnd ſage dem <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l7">ſıe das pferd <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıdergebe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Sıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> Vns auch dabey geſagt . <expan>vv<ex>er</ex>e</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l8"><expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> der das Pferd <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hett . ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe das pferd vmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l9">gots wıllen <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo mag der <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> Vnſers <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l10"><expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / des das pferd ſol ſeyn in kürcʒ ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l11"><expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürderlıch darinn ſeyn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_r1l12">als vıl vns gebürt / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_333_line_1577277937003_1497">etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>ıp<ex>ſ</ex>a</expan> dıe <expan>ſ<ex>anc</ex>tı</expan> gallȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Raban Hofwart von Kircheim, unsers <expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wirczburg
                            <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> einr <expan>im<ex>m</ex></expan> her vor Sacz
                        ein pferd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lorn</expan> und der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> einr das
                            <expan>aufgefange<ex>n</ex></expan> süll <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu was uns desmals niht wissend davon,
                        so waren auch die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> awsz dem her dennoch niht
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, also <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir seid
                        umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> fleissig darnach fragen lassen <pb facs="#facs_333" id="165v"/> und ist uns zu
                        wissen <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz etlich der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein fremd pferd haben, mit den
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir davon reden lassen, die
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, wie in <expan>im<ex>m</ex></expan> her
                        ein fremd pfeͣrd <expan>zugeloffe<ex>n</ex></expan> keͣme, das
                                <expan>fienge<ex>n</ex></expan> sie auf und
                            <expan>weste<ex>n</ex></expan> niht, wes es
                        <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, und <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie
                        allweg in der meynung <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch noch seyn,
                                <expan>kom<ex>m</ex></expan> der, des das pferd sey,
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der des ware
                            <expan>worczaiche<ex>n</ex></expan> bring und sage, dem
                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> sie das pferd
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>widergebe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Sie <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> uns
                        auch dabey gesagt, <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>nyema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, der das pferd
                            <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hett, so
                            <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> sie das pferd umb gots willen
                                <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, also mag der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> unsers
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, des das pferd sol seyn, in kürcz zu uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> oder <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürderlich darinn seyn, als vil uns gebürt.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>anc</ex>ti</expan> Galli.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
